I was 5 or 6 and was around 1 in the morning when I experienced it. I remember waking up for no reason and looking around the room half asleep. The room, lit by my night light and television, had this weird feeling like something was scolding me. I saw this thing in my doorway that looked like a 7 foot man but its body was completely pitch black. I Remember blacking out and having a lucid dream than waking up than being forced down in the bed by a pressure in my chest. After that night I always felt like I was being watched in my bedroom so keeping the lights on at night was what put me to sleep.
